title: Thom Hartmann Program - November 26 2013
description:
November 26, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 

Hour One: What Would Jesus Do...with the banksters?  Peter Schiff, The Peter Schiff Show / Plus, are spanked children more likely to be criminals?

Hour Two: What would you call this Do-Nothing Congress?  David Bender, Progressive Voices

Hour Three: Absused by the TSA?  There's an app for that - Rajdeep Singh, The Sikh Coalition
